description: Teebsie pops are the perfect SoCal summer treats, with deliciously creative flavors made with locally sourced organic ingredients, unrefined sugars, and they’re all dairy-free. You can delight in their selection of flavors like Hibiscus Watermelon, Espresso Cardamom, Lavender Earl Grey, Basil Mint Chocolate, and more. If you’re throwing a big party, be sure to invite the Teebsie mobile pop trike so that your guests can refresh themselves under the beaming California sunlight in the tastiest way possible.
name: Teebsie
